msgid ""
"Join the Crush.lu coaching team. Host events, verify members in person, "
"facilitate connections, and help singles in Luxembourg meet face-to-face. "
"Flexible hours, full training provided."
msgstr ""
"Rejoins l'équipe de coaching de Crush.lu. Organise des événements, vérifie "
"les membres en personne, facilite les connexions et aide les célibataires du"
" Luxembourg à se rencontrer en personne. Horaires flexibles, formation "
"complète."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:10
msgid ""
"crush coach, volunteer dating coach, luxembourg singles, coach recruitment, "
"crush.lu team, dating event host"
