#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:98
msgid "Flexible Hours"
msgstr "Horaires flexibles"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:99
msgid "Work on Your Schedule"
msgstr "Travaillez à votre rythme"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:106
msgid "Why Become a Coach?"
msgstr "Pourquoi devenir Coach ?"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:107
msgid ""
"Coaching is more than a role — it's a chance to shape Luxembourg's dating "
"culture."
msgstr ""
"Le coaching est bien plus qu'un rôle — c'est l'occasion de façonner la "
"culture des rencontres au Luxembourg."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:112
msgid "Make a Real Difference"
msgstr "Faites une vraie différence"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:113
msgid ""
"You'll be the first person to welcome new members. Your feedback helps them "
"put their best foot forward and find real connections."
msgstr ""
"Vous serez la première personne à accueillir les nouveaux membres. Vos "
"retours les aident à se présenter sous leur meilleur jour et à trouver de "
"vraies connexions."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:117
msgid "Flexible & Remote"
msgstr "Flexible & à distance"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:118
msgid ""
"Host events when it suits you, and handle quick tasks from anywhere — answer"
" a member's question or review a connection request between meetings."
msgstr ""
"Anime des événements quand ça t'arrange et gère de petites tâches depuis "
"n'importe où — réponds à la question d'un membre ou examine une demande de "
"connexion entre deux réunions."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:122
msgid "Grow Your Skills"
msgstr "Développez vos compétences"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:123
msgid ""
"Develop your listening, coaching, and communication skills. Get early access"
" to new features and be part of shaping the platform."
msgstr ""
"Développez vos compétences d'écoute, de coaching et de communication. "
"Accédez en avant-première aux nouvelles fonctionnalités et participez à "
"façonner la plateforme."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:131
msgid "What You'll Do"
msgstr "Ce que vous ferez"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:132
msgid ""
"A mix of tasks that keep things interesting — no two days are the same."
msgstr "Un mélange de tâches variées — aucun jour ne se ressemble."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:138
msgid "Verify New Members"
msgstr "Vérifier les nouveaux membres"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:139
msgid ""
"Verify new members in person when they arrive at an event — a quick, "
"friendly face-to-face is all it takes."
msgstr ""
"Vérifie les nouveaux membres en personne à leur arrivée à un événement — un "
"échange rapide et chaleureux suffit."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:145
msgid "Host & Welcome at Events"
msgstr "Animer & accueillir aux événements"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:146
msgid ""
"Welcome members at events, explain how things work, and set a warm, safe "
"tone for everyone."
msgstr ""
"Accueille les membres aux événements, explique comment ça marche et instaure"
" une ambiance chaleureuse et sûre pour tous."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:152
msgid "Manage Event Check-ins"
msgstr "Gérer les check-ins d'événements"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:153
msgid ""
"Use our QR code system to check attendees in at events quickly and smoothly."
msgstr ""
"Utilisez notre système de QR codes pour enregistrer les participants aux "
"événements rapidement et facilement."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:159
msgid "Facilitate Connections"
msgstr "Faciliter les connexions"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:160
msgid ""
"Help mutual matches connect after events. Review connection requests and "
"mediate introductions."
msgstr ""
"Aidez les matches mutuels à se connecter après les événements. Examinez les "
"demandes de connexion et facilitez les présentations."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:166
msgid "Guide Member Journeys"
msgstr "Accompagner les parcours membres"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:167
msgid ""
"Support members through interactive experiences, challenges, and seasonal "
"campaigns."
msgstr ""
"Accompagnez les membres à travers des expériences interactives, des défis et"
" des campagnes saisonnières."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:173
msgid "Ongoing Member Support"
msgstr "Support continu des membres"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:174
msgid ""
"Answer questions, address concerns, and ensure every member feels welcome "
"and supported."
msgstr ""
"Répondez aux questions, traitez les préoccupations et assurez-vous que "
"chaque membre se sente bienvenu et soutenu."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:183
msgid "Who We're Looking For"
msgstr "Qui nous recherchons"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:188
msgid "Empathetic and non-judgmental — you enjoy helping people"
msgstr "Empathique et bienveillant(e) — vous aimez aider les gens"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:189
msgid "Multilingual — comfortable in at least 2 of EN, DE, FR"
msgstr "Multilingue — à l'aise dans au moins 2 langues parmi EN, DE, FR"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:190
msgid "Reliable — you follow through on commitments"
msgstr "Fiable — vous tenez vos engagements"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:191
msgid "Connected to Luxembourg — you live in or know the community"
msgstr "Connecté(e) au Luxembourg — vous y vivez ou connaissez la communauté"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:197
msgid ""
"No experience required — we'll train you on everything you need to know."
msgstr ""
"Aucune expérience requise — nous vous formons sur tout ce qu'il faut savoir."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:200
msgid "2-4 hours per week"
msgstr "2-4 heures par semaine"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:201
msgid "Fully remote (events are optional)"
msgstr "Entièrement à distance (événements optionnels)"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:202
msgid "Volunteer role with perks"
msgstr "Rôle bénévole avec avantages"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:203
msgid "Full onboarding and training provided"
msgstr "Intégration et formation complètes"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:212
msgid "Ready to Make a Difference?"
msgstr "Prêt(e) à faire la différence ?"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:213
msgid "We're all about real human connection and that starts with your voice!"
msgstr ""
"Chez nous, tout tourne autour de la vraie connexion humaine et ça commence "
"par votre voix !"

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:215
msgid ""
"No hiding behind emails. Pick up the phone, call us, and convince us why "
"you'd make an amazing coach. If you can charm us, imagine what you'll do for"
" our members."
msgstr ""
"Pas question de se cacher derrière des emails. Décrochez le téléphone, "
"appelez-nous et convainquez-nous pourquoi vous feriez un coach incroyable. "
"Si vous arrivez à nous charmer, imaginez ce que vous ferez pour nos membres."

#: templates/crush_lu/crush_coach.html:224
msgid "We're happy to answer any questions about coaching."
msgstr "Nous répondons volontiers à toutes vos questions sur le coaching."

